Package: ntrd
Type: Package
Title: Neuropsychological Test Results Dashboard
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Description: Building on the ntrs package,
    this package includes a Shiny application that makes 
    it easy to present test scores in a way useful
    to consensus diagnosis. Data can be imported as a
    .csv file, or extensions can be created to import
    directly from REDCap/any other database system accessible
    via API.
